markets.title: BOY CRAZY streams by May 23, 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If BOY CRAZY by Kesha has above 1 million total streams on Spotify on May 23, 2025 at 10 AM ET, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Total stream count will be determined using the Spotify desktop app at 10 AM ET, based on the exact number displayed at that time. Any updates or changes after 10 AM ET will NOT be considered. The following song can be found here: https://open.spotify.com/track/5CiPDLxXmUG7Fk5yjlNy9n?si=b79945d72b4e4e47
